{"tid":2440954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港Ig閪女人唔係賣鬼仔邪教水晶就賣禁藥呃錢 冇後果？少少公義都冇人爭取 唔好同我講理想","createTime":"2021-03-10T10:27:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T09:56:37.000Z","uid":268373,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4ac4e365831d6b360a7ded6530a9e4a6d3f46987","tid":2440954,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:27:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/video/top/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fvideo%2Ftop%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=2efd6b0d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fvideo%2Ftop%2F&h=b1412c74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/video/top/</a><br />\n<br />\n衞生署周二（9日）晚上呼籲市民勿購買或服用減肥產品「金仔減肥藥」，指含禁藥「西布曲明」成份，服後或危害健康。《蘋果》追查發現，近期人氣KOL blackruby曾在網上「獨家」力銷同名減肥藥，因標榜減肥「不瘦胸」而熱賣，兩名曾服該藥事主均稱被blackruby驕人身材吸引而向她買藥，結果經歷慘痛副作用，包括頭暈作嘔、意識模糊、無食慾，甚至自殘，「搣死皮搣到流血」，更有幻覺，感覺恍如活在電影《廿二世紀殺人網絡》情節，「分辨唔到邊樣先係現實」，有事主更因此令焦慮症復發。她們奉勸想減肥女生三思，別以為靠藥減肥很輕鬆，「錢事小，但身體壞咗就係壞咗，要調理返好，仲辛苦過你去減肥。」<br />\n<br />\n涉事人氣KOL blackruby，在社交平台Instagram有逾20萬粉絲追蹤，身材姣好，早前以自己作招徠，開設IG Shop售賣減肥豐胸產品。上月中，有人將服藥後不適經歷放上網上討論區連登後，她同月21日起停售減肥藥。記者透過Instagram聯絡她欲問事件回應，惟她未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n條廢柴口講唔理人點講佢 又咪係淆撚到del晒野 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gFjdfwd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgFjdfwd.png&h=e2a9c2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\">張硯秋你洗你啲污糟錢果時個心有冇痛呀<br />\n<span class=\"red\">呃o靚妹錢唔理人地身體健康當人戇鳩 為賺快錢不擇手段 我都味見過人咁撚賤</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/video/top/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fvideo%2Ftop%2F&h=bd51ee8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8GYBddb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8GYBddb.png&h=14e96260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">聲大夾惡咁撚串 唔正面回應記者？行得正企得正，怕乜呀張硯秋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\nP.s. 真女神 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qrqzKkg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqrqzKkg.png&h=44cbaa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">支那ding_2當自己Followers 戇鳩賣水晶昆水</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"large\">屌你求鳩其搵個廣東話講唔正，講到1999既呀嬸大陸就當法師 咪撚玩我啦<br />\n個呀嬸：lee個既....就開過光既...就好啲嫁，冇開光冇咁好...既....</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iKqcv1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiKqcv1a.png&h=f8695e6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4n6bMzA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4n6bMzA.png&h=761e1ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢自己打段咁既野出嚟果陣有冇偷笑呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYXqQ1H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYXqQ1H.png&h=0e5ba9ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\">係到戴定頭盔：haha我一開頭都以為佢係膠珠... 咪撚玩啦 明眼人睇你啲所謂水晶都知質素如何啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsNFEVw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsNFEVw.png&h=985e6eda&s={SIZE}\" /></span><br />\n[gold]<span class=\"x-large\">最撚好笑係呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你成日扮晒：呀我地又同師傅呀 尼泊爾果邊傾好生意呀 1000蚊減500蚊呀～ 買一送一呀 咪撚笑死人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>[gold]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TBrAuo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TBrAuo.png&h=5c01c09b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">多謝盛惠人仔$8 多謝晒你地水魚比錢我過風流生活 香港真係冇窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bOf4m9K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbOf4m9K.png&h=52cd6558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n:<span class=\"x-large\">HER TAOBAO STORE</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n7NFEWB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn7NFEWB.png&h=f7d81f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唉，我都想好似dingding 咁求期搵個大媽扮法師 呢舊膠又開左光保財運，果條繩又念過咒有法力 輕輕鬆鬆十鳩幾萬一個月 爽呀<br />\n<br />\n最後：<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">BlackRuby條撚樣唔坐監我退出連登</span></span>"},{"pid":"cb559e4c4902433a5b20041452477939b1a555fe","tid":2440954,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:28:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"168e9dafe8225bb46581ed28598ca4f3c2583e11","tid":2440954,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1254faff178059860bff78d6e20bcd254a4542","tid":2440954,"uid":268373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T10:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 